Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.33,1:01:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你不饿了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.40,1:01:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.40,1:01:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么不讲不知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.34,1:02:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,坂咲要不要去买点东西    还是要出去吃
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.04,1:02:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那要吃什么好呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.42,1:02:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,吃披萨吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.34,1:02:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想出去吃披萨
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.52,1:02:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那吃什么
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.59,1:02:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在家随便煮点东西吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.20,1:02:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.36,1:02:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 可以啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.36,1:02:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.43,1:02:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啦 可能很脏
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.43,1:02:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不会怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.43,1:02:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你要煮吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.37,1:02:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.44,1:02:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.44,1:02:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我先去看看有什么
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.45,1:02:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊 好像不错
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.45,1:02:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,坂咲酱厨房很脏的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.39,1:02:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系我会整理的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.39,1:02:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.33,1:03:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.40,1:03:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.40,1:03:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.41,1:03:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚做便当了 刚刚做了便当是吗                                                        
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.34,1:03:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.41,1:03:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.41,1:03:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,坂咲酱 今天很高兴嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.41,1:03:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,高兴？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.41,1:03:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,看你的样子很高兴
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.43,1:03:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,坂咲酱在这之前我跟你玩个游戏
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.43,1:03:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,穿这件衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.43,1:03:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么   围裙啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.44,1:03:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么会有啊 什么时候买的？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.37,1:03:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为了今天准备的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.44,1:03:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那个    什么   外遇了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.45,1:03:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.45,1:03:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真可疑
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.38,1:03:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能有
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.45,1:03:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这个     很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.38,1:03:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,很适合你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.80,1:03:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,, 可疑
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.39,1:04:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有 就是给你买的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.33,1:04:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.80,1:04:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要穿？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.40,1:04:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,穿上去
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.34,1:04:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.40,1:04:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.34,1:04:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,坂咲酱穿围裙就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.34,1:04:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,穿围裙就好 什么意思
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.63,1:04:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只穿围裙
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.41,1:04:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,里面的内衣脱掉
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.35,1:04:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这样比较好看
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.42,1:04:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.35,1:04:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.56,1:04:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,里面不要穿了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.36,1:04:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 不要啦  好害羞
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.20,1:04:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,坂咲酱
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.03,1:04:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞 
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.37,1:04:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,坂咲酱  我看你害羞的样子很兴奋
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.44,1:04:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.38,1:04:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,穿围裙就好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.45,1:05:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是是的呢  坂咲酱这样比较好看
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.45,1:05:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那我换换
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.39,1:05:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我去房间换
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.43,1:05:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.40,1:05:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.33,1:05:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里换？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.43,1:05:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对  在这换
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.34,1:05:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以看哟
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.41,1:05:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.41,1:05:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.41,1:05:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.42,1:05:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对适合你
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.35,1:05:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,11111111111111111111
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.42,1:05:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.42,1:05:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.36,1:05:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可以啦 可疑
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.37,1:05:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不要一直看
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.37,1:06:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有看 你看了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.38,1:06:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那转过去就不害羞
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.45,1:06:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一样啊 不一样
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.33,1:06:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好近 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.40,1:06:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好近
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.34,1:06:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好变态啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.41,1:06:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不讨厌吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.36,1:06:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.36,1:06:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.37,1:07:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不想讲
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.44,1:07:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,很好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.38,1:07:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,太超过了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.38,1:07:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.45,1:07:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.41,1:07:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要穿啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.41,1:07:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,都脱掉
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.35,1:07:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.42,1:07:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次这样
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.43,1:08:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很合适 这颜色
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.36,1:08:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.37,1:08:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这样有意义吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.37,1:08:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.44,1:08:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,先穿上啦
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.38,1:08:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,穿这就没有意义了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.39,1:08:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,挡不住啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.32,1:08:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,会跑出来
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.33,1:08:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,都看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.40,1:08:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.34,1:08:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.34,1:08:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.34,1:08:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.35,1:08:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 害羞
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.35,1:08:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.42,1:08:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,后面呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.43,1:09:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这样 什么
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.36,1:09:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.44,1:09:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,翘高屁股 为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.38,1:09:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,翘啦
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.38,1:09:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,动一下
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.45,1:09:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.39,1:09:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.40,1:09:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很可爱啦
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.34,1:09:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,动一下
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.41,1:09:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,看太多了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.34,1:09:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.35,1:10:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,还想看
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.35,1:10:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,看什么
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.42,1:10:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,往前面弯
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.43,1:10:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看不到啦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.36,1:10:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.37,1:10:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这样煮东西真棒
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.37,1:10:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,变态
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.45,1:10:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真有趣 哪有
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.39,1:10:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可以挡住啦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.33,1:10:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.40,1:10:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这样呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.40,1:10:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这样用
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.34,1:11:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,看一下
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.34,1:11:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这样呢?  挤一下
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.42,1:11:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.42,1:11:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,还是会看到
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.43,1:11:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊 干嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.44,1:11:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,下面啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.37,1:11:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,里面有东西
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.45,1:11:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么 打开看
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.45,1:11:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.32,1:11:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.40,1:12:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这边会有啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.41,1:12:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就为了这一刻
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.34,1:12:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.35,1:12:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.35,1:12:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,用这做吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.42,1:12:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 我饿了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.43,1:12:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,吃这个
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.36,1:12:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.43,1:12:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一下下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.33,1:13:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.33,1:13:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,进去点 真棒
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.34,1:13:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,舔下面 对
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.43,1:13:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 哪有
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.44,1:13:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好性感
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.45,1:13:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.41,1:14:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真变态
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.41,1:14:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好变态啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.42,1:14:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,还想要吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.42,1:14:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.43,1:14:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,问我
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.43,1:14:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是想吃你
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.43,1:14:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,说啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.37,1:14:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.44,1:14:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可以啦
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.44,1:14:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,来吃我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.45,1:15:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那我开动了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.41,1:15:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 插了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.42,1:15:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,插了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.37,1:15:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.38,1:16:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这吗？ 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.33,1:16:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.34,1:16:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.34,1:16:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,还要吗？还要
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.42,1:16:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 去了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.37,1:16:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.44,1:17:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.38,1:17:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.45,1:17:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.38,1:17:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,太无趣了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.46,1:17:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 我想更色一点
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.32,1:17:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.39,1:17:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这给你 打开脚
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.33,1:17:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.40,1:17:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,打开脚
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.34,1:17:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗？ 嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.34,1:17:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这样才看得清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.35,1:17:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞啦
